@startuml
autonumber

box "Orchestration Layer" #LightCyan
participant "Camunda Engine" as Camunda
participant "Kong Gateway" as Kong
end box

box "Microservice Layer" #LightYellow
participant "UtilityOperator MS" as UOMS
participant "Prosumer MS" as PMS
participant "AssetLink MS" as ALMS
participant "Telemetry MS" as TMS
participant "Grid Balancing MS" as GBMS
end box

box "Messaging Layer" #Thistle
queue "Kafka Topic:\nGridBalancingRecommendation" as Kafka
end box

box "Persistence Layer" #LightGreen
database "AWS RDS" as DB
end box

== Data Gathering Phase (Camunda Orchestration) ==

Camunda -> Kong: GET /UtilityOperator/gridcell
Kong -> UOMS: Forward GET /UtilityOperator/gridcell
UOMS -> DB: JDBC SELECT Grid Cells
DB --> UOMS: Results
UOMS --> Kong: 200 OK (Grid Cells List)
Kong --> Camunda: 200 OK (Grid Cells Data)

Camunda -> Kong: GET /Prosumer
Kong -> PMS: Forward GET /Prosumer
PMS -> DB: JDBC SELECT Prosumers
DB --> PMS: Results
PMS --> Kong: 200 OK (Prosumers List)
Kong --> Camunda: 200 OK (Prosumers Data)

Camunda -> Kong: GET /AssetLink
Kong -> ALMS: Forward GET /AssetLink
ALMS -> DB: JDBC SELECT Asset Links
DB --> ALMS: Results
ALMS --> Kong: 200 OK (Asset Links List)
Kong --> Camunda: 200 OK (Asset Links Data)

Camunda -> Kong: GET /Telemetry
Kong -> TMS: Forward GET /Telemetry
TMS -> DB: JDBC SELECT Telemetry
DB --> TMS: Results
TMS --> Kong: 200 OK (Telemetry Data)
Kong --> Camunda: 200 OK (Telemetry Data)

== Grid Balancing Evaluation ==

Camunda -> Kong: POST /GridBalancingRecommendation/evaluate\n{telemetryData: [...], gridCells: [...]}
Kong -> GBMS: Forward POST /evaluate

GBMS -> GBMS: Analyze aggregated data \nacross Grid Zones
note right
  1. Calculate current load vs capacity per GridCell.
  2. If a Zone exceeds its safety threshold,
     scan neighbouring zones for surplus.
  3. Formulate Balancing Recommendation.
end note

GBMS -> DB: JDBC INSERT INTO BalancingRecommendation\n(sourceGridCellId, targetGridCellId, sourceNetLoadKw, \ntargetHeadroomKw, overloadKw, transferableKw, ...)
DB --> GBMS: 200 OK

GBMS -> Kafka: Publish GridBalancingRecommendation \nEvent {sourceGridCellId, \ntargetGridCellId, ntransferableKw, ...}
Kafka --> GBMS: Ack

GBMS --> Kong: 200 OK (Array of Recommendations)
Kong --> Camunda: Evaluation Complete

== Continuous Event Consumption ==

loop continuous polling
    UOMS -> Kafka: Consume from GridBalancingRecommendation
    Kafka --> UOMS: JSON Payload
    note right of UOMS: Utility Operator consumes recommendation for execution/action.
end
@enduml